### HYMN III

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_2000301">1</span></span>Come, we
have pressed the juice for thee: O Indra, drink this  
  Soma here.  
  Seat thee on this my sacred grass.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_2000302">2</span></span>Let both thy
bay steeds, yoked by prayer long-maned, O Indra,  
   bring thee nigh.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_2000303">3</span></span>We
Soma-bearing Brāhmans call thee Soma-drinker with thy  
   friend,  
  We, Indra, who have pressed the juice.

